{"tid":955184,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"後民主社會仲有咩可以重大進步","createTime":"2018-12-25T07:58:30.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-25T16:41:26.000Z","uid":171572,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"6adffb3d529e8afbd0a52ee08806455a7a5d1212","tid":955184,"uid":171572,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-25T07:58:30.000Z","msg":"即係美國北歐西歐日本咁，民主已有，但依然問題多多。放眼人類咁睇，仲可以點再上一層，未到呢個層次的地方就免談啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd0ee564148adb26b808f79bd4d4f3e3b121c171","tid":955184,"uid":171572,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-25T08:03:55.000Z","msg":"先進民主國家嘅工業同農業生產力好似完全滿足曬人類需求，只係分配上有問題，所以依然好多窮人<br />\n<br />\n其實挪威底層生活有無尊嚴？"},{"pid":"f7fba9feef325aff22a6a0ecee81aca6f368fb94","tid":955184,"uid":171572,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-25T08:08:00.000Z","msg":"日本仔大把月光，租唔起樓，永遠單身，食物好撚貴，幾乎滿足唔到食慾，想食多兩個橙都唔得呀屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n美國醫療霸權，睇醫生會破產，警察又霸權，無生命保障，大把人瞓下水道偷呃拐騙"},{"pid":"2fe7c583d83f6f6a57d5ca9590ba2641c5ceab8f","tid":955184,"uid":116630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-25T08:15:25.000Z","msg":"&ldquo;Democracy is the worst form of government, except for all the others.&rdquo;"},{"pid":"22a071075fca22b8f918b69b0c1ad7210c0fc3af","tid":955184,"uid":171572,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2fe7c583d83f6f6a57d5ca9590ba2641c5ceab8f","tid":955184,"uid":116630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-25T08:15:25.000Z","msg":"&ldquo;Democracy is the worst form of government, except for all the others.&rdquo;"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-25T08:21:04.000Z","msg":"但依家係先肯定民主再討論，係其於最發達的地區再討論。<br />\n<br />\n你講民主咪拉返落中國東南亞lv囉，返返正題先好嗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f85bcf6eb8a7db5eed9e0d8d4849ddc3d8d63bf","tid":955184,"uid":81424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-25T11:40:23.000Z","msg":"唔知算唔算得上進步<br />\n但無條件基本收入姑且算其中一樣<br />\n<br />\n美國就大把野講嘅<br />\n敎育資源分配/學區制/大學學費/醫療/窮人地區嘅治安"},{"pid":"e0886a25c72ec382414f6d6fde193c117679e692","tid":955184,"uid":171572,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0f85bcf6eb8a7db5eed9e0d8d4849ddc3d8d63bf","tid":955184,"uid":81424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-25T11:40:23.000Z","msg":"唔知算唔算得上進步<br />\n但無條件基本收入姑且算其中一樣<br />\n<br />\n美國就大把野講嘅<br />\n敎育資源分配/學區制/大學學費/醫療/窮人地區嘅治安"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-25T11:47:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 贊同，andrew yang<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c466edee1f21eb35e271aad1f66f9803e31ba63f","tid":955184,"uid":3342,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-25T16:34:51.000Z","msg":"與其話係民主問題，其實樓主所講嘅更加似係資本主義問題"},{"pid":"5e3752d06da845261a526e9ee449e7f132a56db4","tid":955184,"uid":115510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-25T16:41:26.000Z","msg":"政治既本質就係利益既分配<br />\n民主既社會面對資本主義產生既貧富不均現象<br />\n我地應該關心<br />\n點樣做大個餅令更多人受益<br />\n點樣讓勤奮既窮人向上流動<br />\n點樣達致一個更公義社會<br />\n我覺得會係著眼點"}]}